Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.85,0:00:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.68,0:00:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.39,0:00:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.36,0:00:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.14,0:00:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.95,0:00:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.62,0:00:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.99,0:00:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.09,0:01:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.70,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.14,0:01:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.81,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.18,0:01:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.72,0:01:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.67,0:01:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於進入大學聯考的考季
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.50,0:01:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過居然報考這麼多所大學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有精神值得讚許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.27,0:02:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,考不上的還是考不上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.61,0:02:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說你們啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.61,0:02:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,皮膚暗沈粗糙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鼻頭也乾乾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.41,0:02:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舌頭也缺乏光澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體狀況不太好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少在這裡胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.69,0:02:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來是第二看好\N今天要考的N大說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.46,0:02:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概不可能了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.26,0:02:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我賭全部都考不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.77,0:02:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在看不出來\N有哪一所他一定能考上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.67,0:02:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#04 響子緊張萬分?五代考試中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有東西忘了帶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都帶齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准考證帶了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.92,0:02:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,當然有帶囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天考的是N大吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的,我的安全牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.40,0:03:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是K大的准考證嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次一定沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我會加油的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我會加油的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你找死啊你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我會加油的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.69,0:04:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我會加油的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.13,0:04:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一天就這樣\N接下來真令人擔心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員,妳偏心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這麼關心那個重考生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.11,0:04:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年紀小的或許也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.67,0:04:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下,你們在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.31,0:04:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳愛上那個重考生了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在胡說些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.16,0:04:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.69,0:04:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員關心房客是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果五代今年又落榜的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們大家也有責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員真的生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.35,0:05:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(五代,請加油喔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我會加油的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一天慘敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜…拜託,還沒放榜啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.76,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,考不上的啦,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天考不上,還有明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亂槍掃射總會掃中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.37,0:05:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照這樣一路落榜下去吧\N我賺爆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.81,0:06:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣根本不是在鼓勵我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.31,0:06:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不是因為聽了\N朱美說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.68,0:06:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的大學入學考試連續慘敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.05,0:06:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒考的學校\N也沒剩下幾所了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.66,0:06:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我會加油的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我會加油的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你午飯吃了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代不曉得考得還順利嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五…五代,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.14,0:07:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重考生經常摸妳的屁股嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.21,0:07:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一之瀨太太\N請不要開這種惡質的玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.78,0:07:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我看妳的屁股蠻不錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.01,0:07:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一定可以生很多\N健康的寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.69,0:07:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等一下拿茶點去妳那裡坐坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…等一下,一之瀨太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相親?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.20,0:08:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.60,0:08:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一大堆喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個醫生喔,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.01,0:08:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個男生長得很帥吧\N聽說是K大畢業的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳聽我說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳不喜歡嗎?\N想不到妳還蠻挑的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,這個如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,累死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.26,0:08:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好拼一拼\N剩下比較有希望的學校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳到底喜歡\N哪一類型的男人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.24,0:08:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去相一次親有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.87,0:08:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.44,0:08:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並沒有打算要結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?\N妳已經到了適婚年齡了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有喜歡的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說呢\N好像有,又好像沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.56,0:09:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底有沒有?快說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是妳還沒有下定決心嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說是\N我還沒做好心理準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個男人在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一直都在我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他非常地愛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.35,0:09:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很愛他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.92,0:09:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把惣一郎的事說出來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這麼愛那個重考生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.86,0:09:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真…真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼妳會提到五代呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽妳這麼說\N總覺得他最吻合啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.81,0:09:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且妳好像\N老是很在意那個重考生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.58,0:09:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哪裡在意他了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.54,0:10:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才還大叫一聲\N啊!五代!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不要再說了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.82,0:10:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?她大喊我的名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.05,0:10:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過妳還是放棄他比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為那傢伙毫無前途可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.09,0:10:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管他再怎麼好運\N頂多也只能進二流大學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又沒有一技之長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意志也薄弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年紀又比妳小,根本靠不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.81,0:10:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳沒必要把他\N說得這麼一文不值吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重考一次是很平常的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.88,0:10:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他待人親切,是個好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.59,0:10:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人最重要的是內在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.19,0:10:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
