Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.11,0:11:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧\N我不會跟重考生說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這小子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.96,0:11:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你都聽到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真受不了\N怎麼有你這種男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傻瓜,我幹嘛臉紅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣反而會被誤會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎,原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,怎麼有你這種男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然會在走廊偷聽\N女人之間的談話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.05,0:11:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.39,0:11:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為妳的聲音太大聲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想聽也聽得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.49,0:11:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你需要貼在門板上聽嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊!就是啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.23,0:12:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你不明白\N管理員的用心良苦嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的要我明說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.21,0:12:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為她愛著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.81,0:12:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才會這麼辛苦地保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.51,0:12:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大學聯考的緊要關頭\N她不想讓你分心動搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.86,0:12:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.84,0:12:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這個誤會太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.40,0:13:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨,我去上學囉,惣一郎
