Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什麼時候才要走啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.95,0:13:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的學校你最有把握不是嗎?\N快要遲到囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.72,0:13:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.59,0:13:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿你沒輒,等一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.59,0:13:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.91,0:13:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不可以再被誤會下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看,妳看\N那是典型的考生打扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好呆喔,一定是重考生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
