Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.59,0:14:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,恭喜你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了恭喜你金榜題名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不嫌棄接受我的吻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來今年也完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,T大前站,T大前站\N電車馬上就要開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.45,0:15:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經寫完了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是個心胸狹窄的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.11,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天明明是他最重要的考試…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他現在可能正在考試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.48,0:16:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.42,0:16:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你誤會了啦,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.29,0:16:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是以管理員的身分\N為五代加油…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.47,0:16:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外沒有任何的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.30,0:16:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你相信我,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是什麼關係啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.98,0:16:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路上賣藝的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.31,0:16:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是打電話給衛生局比較好吧\N這種事很難說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.68,0:16:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是另類的外遇嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.05,0:16:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會是彩券中了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.79,0:16:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到底是怎麼了…
