Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.91,0:17:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了慶祝本店開張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.35,0:17:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別舉辦血拼大相送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.65,0:17:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真傻\N五代怎麼可能會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.34,0:17:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生,請不要做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.91,0:17:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,我真的太在意他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.05,0:17:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這也是身為管理員的職責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!妳誤會了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我誤會什麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.37,0:18:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,進來進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這家店我很熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我不想在大白天就喝酒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要坐哪裡好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.49,0:18:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐桌子那裡吧,那裡比較舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼響子會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.99,0:18:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先來大杯的啤酒\N還有魚肉丸跟烤魷魚兩人份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.33,0:18:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生,你身體不舒服嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有其它的出口嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有那裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.31,0:18:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喝吧,有心事的時候喝酒最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有心事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳很在意早上的事,不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.68,0:19:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是很單純地\N擔心五代考試的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,純愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好酒量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是管理員耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,再來一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道管理員不可以關心房客嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐,妳還沒付錢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的只是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.77,0:19:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.44,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去一下洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.57,0:20:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.84,0:20:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.38,0:20:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕,我忘了香煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.15,0:20:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在他正在考下午的科目吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.66,0:20:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快要醉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去一下洗手間吧\N我們還要繼續喝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.70,0:20:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.88,0:21:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.37,0:21:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你在這裡幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.64,0:21:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為題目實在太難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想說這下死定了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.22,0:21:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你中途跑出來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還用問嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.15,0:21:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他都已經在這裡吃飯了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.12,0:21:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.43,0:21:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣死我了!真的氣死我了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.93,0:22:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.27,0:22:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一次考試,我會跟著你去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.17,0:22:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會一直盯著你\N不讓你中途落跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等,請等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我又不是小孩子,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.21,0:22:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行為明明就是小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.35,0:22:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能放著你不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.65,0:22:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了沒,就這麼決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.99,0:22:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.90,0:22:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,她是你的誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.54,0:22:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦,因為她說她一定要跟來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.81,0:22:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,雖然我問了很多次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.95,0:22:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.28,0:22:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的有說我要來陪考嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.79,0:22:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說得非常肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.45,0:22:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一之瀨大嬸可以作證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.42,0:23:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多該進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.79,0:23:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,拜託妳再對我說那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.17,0:23:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得今天一定會很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.61,0:23:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你的背包…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.82,0:23:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豬頭,大豬頭\N你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.52,0:23:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.33,0:23:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺真像個不中用的弟弟\N真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.34,0:23:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大學聯考落榜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.14,0:23:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重考生跳樓自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.21,0:23:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該…該不會是五代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.75,0:24:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相聚一刻下一回\N『響子焦慮不安!五代離家出走』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.25,0:24:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,請快點回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.12,0:24:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信你會考上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.24,0:24:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.59,0:24:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.63,0:24:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能讓我悸動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.76,0:24:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我身陷險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.87,0:24:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明已經可以相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.45,0:25:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偏偏時機還不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.82,0:25:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快要忍受不了\N快要變成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.36,0:25:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是痛苦的折磨

